objectiv_bach.SeriesGlobalContexts.gc¶

property SeriesGlobalContexts.gc¶

Accessor for Objectiv global context data. All methods of json and objectiv can also be accessed with this accessor. Same as global_contexts

class GlobalContexts(series_object)
property GlobalContexts.application

Returns application id from the global contexts.

property GlobalContexts.cookie_id

Returns cookie id from the global contexts.

property GlobalContexts.user_agent

Returns user agent string from the global contexts.
